doc.title: Diagnosis Murder

credit.role: Dr. Mark Sloan/Gangster John 'Mr. G' Gotti
Dr. Mark Sloan/Jonathan Nash/J. Edison Nash/Judith Nash/Julian Nash

doc.plot: Dr. Mark Sloan is a doctor at Community General Hospital, and he is a consultant for the police department. His son Steve Sloan is a detective for the department. He and his father, along with emergency room resident Dr. Jesse Travis and Dr. Amanda Bentley, who is the pathologist at the hospital help to solve some very strange murder cases in Diagnosis Murder.
